name: Gigpress-for-venues
body: This is a fork of the wonderful [GigPress](https://github.com/amphibian/gigpress). I am currently just playing with some ideas of mutating a version to serve as just an events listing plugin for venues. While the original can do the same thing, I will be changing the workflow based on some requests I have been getting.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
